<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>VAN ZION</title>
<key>E</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Van zion, fanu fapa rual hna tho u sih, Bawipa thangthat u sih
 Kan thazang dihlak chuah in lam usih,
 Kan Pathian thangthat hi a tha bik, Kan Pathiang thangthat hi
 A nuam bik thangthat tlak Jesuh Khrih thangthat uh
 Thangthat uh thangthat chin uh Cungnung bik Bawi.

[C1]
   Sangchin ah, hlor uh Zeizong sertu Bawi cu Pathian hna
   Pathian cu hlorh chin usih, kan damnak le kan zeizong
   Kan zeizong kan Zeizong Bawipa cu thangthat chin usih.

[V2]
 Micheu nih thangthat duh lo hmanseh kan nih cu
 Kan thangthat chinchin lai, Van zion hlathar sa in kan lam lai
 Kan Pathian thangthat hi a tha bik kan pathian thangthat hi
 A nuam bik thangthat tlak Zesuh Khrih, thangthat uh
 Thangthat uh thangthat chin uh Cungnung bik cu.

[V3]
 Kan damnak kan sibawi nganbik le, kan khamh nak kan biaceih
 Bawi nganbik, kan dam kan luatnak Bawi cu thangthat uh
 Kan Pathain thangthat hi a tha bik kan Pathian thangthat hi
 A nuam bik thangthat tlak Jesuh Khrih thangthat uh
 Thangthat uh thangthat chin uh Cungnung bik Bawi.</lyrics>
</song>